text: Jabba may refer to: * Jabba the Hutt, a fictional character in the Star Wars franchise * Jabba (presenter) (Jason Davis, born 1973), Australian actor and media personality * DJ Jabba (Steven Beckford), American DJ and event promoter * JABBA, the Japan Basketball Association * Jabba language, or Hyam language ==See also== * *Jaba (disambiguation) *Jaber (disambiguation) *Jabbawockeez, an American hip-hop dance crew *Jabirr Jabirr, an Indigenous Australian people, sometimes spelt Jabba Jabba
title: Jabba
